en_32453_0	Brigadier N.P Akuranthilake of Sri Lanka Signal Corps (SLSC) assumed office as the new Director of the Army Research Analysis, Projection and Development Branch on Thursday (2) at his office in the Army Cantonment at Panagoda.
en_32453_1	The newly-appointed Director left his signature in an official document and symbolized the acceptance of the new office, amid religious observances.
en_32453_2	Staff officers, Officers and Other Ranks in the Directorate were present at the occasion.
